Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
cvd(25.10)                                                          cvd(25.10)

Name
       cvd

Syntax
        cvd<string>

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Specifies  the  path name to the physical location of the lib/cell/view
       that was "restored" using restoreDesign -cellview. cvd is a  system-de-
       fined,  transient  (non-persistent) global variable used in the OpenAc-
       cess flow. This should be treated as a read-only variable.

Related Information
              * restoreDesign

